3
00:01:26,763 --> 00:01:29,343
Okay, cut! Good, vey good!

4
00:01:29,553 --> 00:01:31,633
Thank you for your hard work. The whole team finished shooting

5
00:01:32,423 --> 00:01:34,093
Chen, your performance in this scene is excellent

6
00:01:34,883 --> 00:01:36,633
When can <i>We</i> return to the Southern Kingdom?

7
00:01:37,133 --> 00:01:38,923
You performed really well

8
00:01:39,763 --> 00:01:41,763
Come, come, take a photo

9
00:01:42,093 --> 00:01:44,003
Hong Dou! Congratulations on finishing the shooting!

10
00:01:45,133 --> 00:01:46,633
