14
00:01:50,593 --> 00:01:51,133
Come, come, come

15
00:01:51,302 --> 00:01:52,212
Thank you for your hard work

16
00:01:52,423 --> 00:01:53,462
You're going over there

17
00:01:53,463 --> 00:01:54,423
I'm here

18
00:01:54,593 --> 00:01:56,303
Look at me, how's my expression?

19
00:01:57,213 --> 00:01:58,633
Congratulations!

20
00:01:58,633 --> 00:01:59,883
Cheese!

21
00:02:04,053 --> 00:02:04,962
Mr. Li

22
00:02:05,383 --> 00:02:07,093
