Jingjing, isn't that your boyfriend?

26
00:02:32,923 --> 00:02:33,712
Mr. Li

27
00:02:34,213 --> 00:02:35,423
Our relationship

28
00:02:35,423 --> 00:02:36,962
doesn't seem that close, does it?

29
00:02:37,263 --> 00:02:38,633
Ms. Hong Dou, you've misunderstood

30
00:02:38,633 --> 00:02:39,963
