38
00:02:55,763 --> 00:02:56,303
Thanks

39
00:03:00,133 --> 00:03:01,013
Interesting

40
00:03:22,673 --> 00:03:24,092
Why is there still no one answering?

41
00:03:36,213 --> 00:03:37,053
Where is this?

42
00:03:39,423 --> 00:03:40,513
Even the most careful plan has a flaw

43
00:03:41,463 --> 00:03:42,263
No matter how much I hate him,

44
00:03:42,923 --> 00:03:44,673
I should have asked him to take<i> Us</i> home

45
00:03:46,463 --> 00:03:49,173
Ye Nanchen, where are you?

46
00:03:50,003 --> 00:03:52,843
<i>We</i>'re lost. Take <i>Us</i> home quickly

47
00:03:55,593 --> 00:03:56,803
Then I'll take you home

48
00:04:47,463 --> 00:04:48,173
Tianxing

49
00:04:51,093 --> 00:04:51,843
Tianxing

50
00:05:04,673 --> 00:05:05,592
Hong Dou

51
