57
00:05:27,003 --> 00:05:28,593
Everything you have is given by me

58
00:05:28,963 --> 00:05:31,053
In three years, I have made you a superstar

59
00:05:31,923 --> 00:05:32,592
Is it not worthy?

60
00:05:33,263 --> 00:05:34,463
Li Tianxing, you bastard

61
00:05:38,673 --> 00:05:39,673
You're just an actress

62
00:05:40,963 --> 00:05:41,883
