63
00:05:57,383 --> 00:05:58,263
Stars

64
00:05:59,303 --> 00:06:00,842
Such bright stars

65
00:06:03,383 --> 00:06:05,923
I am the brightest star

66
00:06:07,763 --> 00:06:09,013
Li Tianxing, what do you mean?

67
00:06:09,463 --> 00:06:11,013
What I mean is already quite clear

68
00:06:13,343 --> 00:06:14,303
Hong Dou

69
00:06:15,883 --> 00:06:16,803
It's all because of you

70
00:06:47,213 --> 00:06:48,383
Is the fireworks in your Southern Kingdom

71
00:06:48,383 --> 00:06:49,343
so beautiful too?

72
00:06:54,513 --> 00:06:55,213
Ye Nanchen

73
00:06:55,263 --> 00:06:56,053
Wait a moment

74
00:07:04,843 --> 00:07:05,463
Hong Dou

75
00:07:07,303 --> 00:07:08,053
I like you,

76
00:07:08,883 --> 00:07:09,843
no matter where you come from,

77
00:07:09,843 --> 00:07:10,883
No matter who you are

78
00:07:12,013 --> 00:07:13,593
Would you like to stay with me forever?
